text: int main ( void ) { int n ; scanf ( "%d" , & n ) ; while ( n -- ) { long long int a , b , i , gcd , lcm ; scanf ( "%lld%lld" , & a , & b ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; ++ i ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) gcd = i ; } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%lld %lld\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
